## 2. 命令路径（本地脚本 vs MCP）

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant Script as 示例脚本
  participant Fluent as ada-fluent / ada_client
  participant Exec as ada-agent executor
  participant Plugin as driver-* 插件
  participant Device as 浏览器 / 真机

  alt 本地 ada-client
    Script->>Fluent: open(browser|device)
    Fluent->>Exec: ada(platform, session, command, payload)
    Exec->>Plugin: CommandEnvelope
    Plugin->>Device: Playwright / adb / WDA / hypium
  else MCP 全程
    Script->>Fluent: open(..., { connect: "mcp" })
    Fluent->>MCPS: ada_web_action / ada_mobile_action
    MCPS->>Exec: 同 CommandEnvelope
    Exec->>Plugin: 同上
  end
```

**原则**：业务脚本只写流利 API（`page.goto` / `phone.fillSearch`）；本地与 MCP 差异仅在传输层。

