## 3. Smart-Wait 与可靠性（框架层）

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  subgraph Mobile["移动 launch / recipe"]
    GOTO["phone.goto(appId)"]
    LAUNCH["launchApp"]
    SW1["custom: smart_wait<br/>launch_settled · 默认上限 8s"]
    FS["recipe fill_search<br/>tap → settle → dump → type"]
    GOTO --> LAUNCH --> SW1
    FS
  end

  subgraph Web["Web 关弹窗"]
    DIS["dismissPopups"]
    PRE["pre: 轮询 blocker<br/>login2025 / dialog"]
    DOM["DOM 扫描 + force-hide"]
    DIS --> PRE --> DOM
  end

  subgraph Core["packages/driver-rpc"]
    SW["smart-wait.ts<br/>timeout · ui_stable · launch_settled"]
    FST["fill-search-transition.ts<br/>页面跳转检测"]
    SW --> SW1
    FST --> FS
  end
```

| 机制 | 位置 | 行为 |
|------|------|------|
| `launch_settled` | `phone.goto` 后 | UI dump 节点数连续稳定即返回；未传 `settleMs` 时上限 **8s**（全平台） |
| `fillSearch` settle | `mobile-recipes.ts` | 跳转检测 + 收紧默认常量；避免 tap/fill 双重长等待 |
| Web pre-wait | `popups.mjs` | dismiss 前探测 `#login2025-dialog-wrap` 等遮挡，再 DOM 关弹窗 |
| 环境变量 | `ADA_WAIT_UNTIL` 等 | 全局覆盖 wait 模式，无需改脚本 |

